  <brief_title>Effect of KW-3902IV in Combination With IV Furosemide on Renal Function in Subjects With CHF and Renal Impairment</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of KW-3902IV in Combination With IV Furosemide on Renal Function in Subjects With Congestive Heart Failure (CHF) and Renal Impairment</official_title>
